**Perfect! ‚úÖ JavaScript fix applied!**

## üéØ **What I've Fixed:**

### **Root Cause Found:**
- **Custom lightbox JavaScript** was displaying ALL fields:
  - Title ‚úÖ (keep)
  - Caption ‚úÖ (keep)  
  - Alt text ‚ùå (causing duplication)
  - Subtitle ‚ùå (causing duplication)
  - Description ‚ùå (causing duplication)

### **Solution Applied:**
```javascript
// Only show title and caption - hide other fields to prevent duplication
lightboxAlt.textContent = '';
lightboxSubtitle.textContent = '';
lightboxDescription.textContent = '';

// Display logic - only show caption, hide everything else
lightboxCaption.style.display = image.caption ? 'block' : 'none';
lightboxAlt.style.display = 'none';        // Always hide alt text
lightboxSubtitle.style.display = 'none';   // Always hide subtitle
lightboxDescription.style.display = 'none'; // Always hide description
```

## üìä **Expected Results:**

**In the lightbox, you'll now see:**
- ‚úÖ **Title** (from WordPress media title field)
- ‚úÖ **Caption** (from WordPress media caption field) - only if it exists
- ‚ùå **No alt text duplication**
- ‚ùå **No description duplication**
- ‚ùå **No subtitle duplication**

**The cards remain perfect** - this only affects the lightbox display!

